OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780646725
OL,3,CRambo knife-wielding man threatens
OL,4,Cwoman then tries to drive wrong way
OL,5,Cdown M5
OL,7,FPictures from West Midlands Police
OL,9,FThis is the chilling moment armed
OL,10,Fofficers captured a knifeman as he
OL,11,Ftried to drive the wrong way down the
OL,12,FM5 after threatening a woman in Dudley.
OL,14,FJoshua Jones made off from police,
OL,15,Fhitting 70mph in a 30mph zone towards
OL,16,Fjunction 2 of the motorway.
OL,18,FHe was being hunted by officers after
OL,19,Fmaking threats to a woman in Halesowen
OL,20,Fearlier in the day while armed with a
OL,21,FRambo-style knife.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780646725
OL,3,CRambo knife-wielding man threatens
OL,4,Cwoman then tries to drive wrong way
OL,5,Cdown M5
OL,7,FAfter being sent to find him, West
OL,8,FMidlands Police officers spotted the
OL,9,Fwhite Ford Puma car he was in off
OL,10,FOldbury Ringway.
OL,12,FThe video shows police pursuing Jones,
OL,13,Fbefore a police car rams into him,
OL,14,Fwhich brought him to a stop. He was
OL,15,Fthen arrested.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780646725
OL,3,CRambo knife-wielding man threatens
OL,4,Cwoman then tries to drive wrong way
OL,5,Cdown M5
OL,7,FChief inspector Sinead Sweeney, head
OL,8,Fof the firearms unit at West Midlands
OL,9,FPolice, said: "This was fantastic
OL,10,Fteamwork by our officers, working
OL,11,Fclosely with NPAS colleagues, who used
OL,12,Ftheir skills and training to bring a
OL,13,Fdangerous offender to justice.
OL,15,F"The consequences of Jones driving the
OL,16,Fwrong way down the motorway could have
OL,17,Fbeen catastrophic.
OL,26,@qD@OOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780646725
OL,3,CRambo knife-wielding man threatens
OL,4,Cwoman then tries to drive wrong way
OL,5,Cdown M5
OL,7,F"Incidents like this just go to show
OL,8,Fthe range of work that firearms
OL,9,Fofficers do, from arresting those
OL,10,Finvolved in gun crime, to pursing
OL,11,Fcriminals armed with other deadly
OL,12,Fweapons on the roads, to supporting
OL,13,Four neighbourhood and investigation
OL,14,Fteams."
OL,16,FThe incident happened at around 10am
OL,17,Fon Sunday, May 24.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780646725
OL,3,CRambo knife-wielding man threatens
OL,4,Cwoman then tries to drive wrong way
OL,5,Cdown M5
OL,7,FFootage from the National Police Air
OL,8,FService helicopter shows how Jones
OL,9,Fdrove the wrong way around the
OL,10,Froundabout and towards oncoming
OL,11,Ftraffic on the slip road of the
OL,12,Fmotorway.
OL,14,FFirearms officers made what they
OL,15,Fdescribed as "tactical contact" with
OL,16,Fthe vehicle to stop it from driving up
OL,17,Fthe wrong side of the motorway.
OL,19,FThe 23-year-old was then arrested, and
OL,20,Fthe Rambo knife recovered from the
OL,21,Fpassenger seat.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780646725
OL,3,CRambo knife-wielding man threatens
OL,4,Cwoman then tries to drive wrong way
OL,5,Cdown M5
OL,7,FJones of Fountain Lane, Oldbury,
OL,8,Fappeared before magistrates in
OL,9,FWolverhampton.
OL,11,FHe admitted possession of a large
OL,12,FRambo knife, dangerous driving,
OL,13,Faggravated vehicle taking, criminal
OL,14,Fdamage to the woman's property and
OL,15,Fusing threatening language to her.
OL,17,FHe was remanded in custody at a
OL,18,Fhearing at the city's crown court on
OL,19,F23 June.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
